wiki.content: ‘Cupid’ is the title track of their 1st Single, The Beginning: Cupid that shows the growth process and the beginning of the four girls. ‘Cupid’ is a retro-style melody reminiscent of a chanson and a faint voice that signals the beginning of the song. In addition, based on minimal disco beats and funky baselines, the song guides the world with Cupid one step at a time through the harmony of subtle vocals and pads. The song shows a cheerful and humorous side through a refreshing synth and melodic piano melody. Sweet vocals show off their loveliness to the fullest, and the tapping rap part adds a rich taste to the song. During the tracking week ending April 1, 2023, the song debuted at #100 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart. During the tracking week ending April 8, 2023, the song reached a new peak of #94 The song marked their first appearance on the Hot 100. Read more on Last.fm.
